wmmp3 - An mpg123 frontend designed for WindowMaker
				Munechika SUMIKAWA <sumikawa@kame.net>
				http://www.kame.net/~sumikawa/wmmp3/

wmmp3 is copyright (c) 1999 by Munechika SUMIKAWA and licensed through
the GNU General Public License.  Read the COPYING file for the
complete GNU license.

--------------------------------------------------------------------
INSTALL:

1. install 'mpg123' first. See, http://mpg.123.org/

2. tar zxvf wmmp3-0.1.tar.gz
   cd wmmp3-0.1
   xmkmf
   make
   su
   make install

--------------------------------------------------------------------
USAGE:

  1. make playlist on ~/.wmmp3

     e.g. mp3 files are installed on /usr/local/data/mp3
       % find /usr/local/data/mp3 -name '*.mp3' > ~/.wmmp3

     NOTE: All filenames are designated as a ABSOLUTELY path.
           And you can also designate URL in ~/.wmmp3

  2. execute wmmp3
       % wmmp3

  3. enjoy!

